longBusinessSummary: MagForce AG operates in the field of nanotechnology-based cancer therapy in Germany and Poland. It offers NanoTherm, a therapy for the treatment of brain tumors; NanoPlan, a software that supports the attending physician in preparing the ideal treatment plan for the NanoTherm therapy; and NanoActivator, a magnetic field generator. MagForce AG was founded in 1997 and is headquartered in Berlin, Germany.
